 </code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>Amends the General Provisions Article of the Illinois Pension Code. </code><code>Provides that Ford Motor Company and its subsidiaries are restricted </code><code>companies. Requires the Illinois Investment Policy Board to make its best </code><code>efforts to identify all subsidiaries of Ford Motor Company and include </code><code>those companies in the list of restricted companies distributed to each </code><code>retirement system and the Illinois State Board of Investment.</code><code>
